#### This contains A Break minigame & A knife minigame
#### **To load it as a prefab**
> Put The .Vmf in folder:
(HardDrive):\Steam\steamapps\*Username*\sourcesdk\bin\orangebox\bin\prefabs

#### **To load it as a map in hammer editor**
> Put The .Vmf (And .Vmx) (.Log is just the compile log) in folder:
(HardDrive):\Steam\steamapps\*Username*\sourcesdk_content\cstrike\mapsrc

#### **To load it as a map in counter-strike:source**
> Put The .bsp in folder:
(HardDrive):\Steam\steamapps\*Username*\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps


**If you use it in your map please give me some credits :)**

#### **Version: 1.0**
To make v2 - Probably A Day. To make V3 - Probably A other day
